{
  "stem": "11144.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- you know, it's interesting because I do ask my friends, and I see very few that do have American friends.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's interesting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is one Jewish woman there in Poland with whom we used to be like this, and our parents were like this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, almost like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then something happened between us and I just-- and now, whenever I went to Poland-- we were just to Poland this summer because I had to go to my mother's grave.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we meet, we are very-- it's very superficial, very superficial.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now on the other hand, I have some Polish friends and I-- I didn't look them up over many, many, many years because, as a [INAUDIBLE], I felt very funny about what I did or whatever.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this summer when I was there, some of them found out that I was there and the phones did not stop ringing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were so excited.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they were going crazy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't stay too long there, so I couldn't see all of them, and unfortunately, our contact was over the phone.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I saw two-- no, I saw four of them, and they were extremely friendly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And extremely-- maybe because I'm in America, too, maybe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think there was a lot going back to our younger days when we were 18 and 19 and 20.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think there was a nostalgia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we really were very-- we spent a lot of time together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were really very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but do I keep up?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do I write to them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, on the other hand, with all our Israeli friends-- I mean, Polish friends that are in Israel, that emigrated-- we are extremely close.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
